<!--
Hugging Face Spaces reads deployment config from YAML frontmatter in the
Space's OWN README.md (a separate repo from this GitHub project — Spaces are
created at huggingface.co/new-space and can pull from a GitHub remote, but
the frontmatter below has to live in the Space repo's README.md itself).

When you create the Space:
  1. SDK: Docker
  2. Point it at Dockerfile.space in this repo (or copy this repo's files in)
  3. Replace this file's target: copy these YAML lines to the Space's
     README.md, adjusting `title`/`emoji` if you like.
-->
---
title: MedClaim Agentic RAG
emoji: 🏥
colorFrom: blue
colorTo: green
sdk: docker
dockerfile: Dockerfile.space
app_port: 7860
pinned: false
---
